{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Wind on Particles"], "type": "title", "extent": [34, 56], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [56, 91], "text": ["Applies wind to particles."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [91, 260], "text": ["Unlike ", {"text": ["POP Force"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popforce", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/dop/popforce"}, ", which continuously accelerates particles, ", {"text": ["POP Wind"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popwind", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/dop/popwind"}, " acts as a drag pulling particles to the ambient wind speed."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [302, 435], "text": ["Click the ", {"text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/POP/wind", "scheme": "Icon", "type": "link", "value": "POP/wind"}, {"text": ["Wind on Particles"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popwind", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/dop/popwind"}, " button on the ", {"text": ["Particles"], "type": "ui"}, " shelf tab."]}, {"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "extent": [556, 703], "text": ["The Wind POP simulates a pushing force like wind, that can increase the velocity of particles but not past its own speed."]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Select the particle system you want to be affected and press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "text": null, "type": "keys"}, " to confirm your selection."], "extent": [435, 556], "blevel": 10, "type": "ord"}, {"indent": 8, "blevel": 10, "type": "ord", "extent": [703, 897], "text": ["Set the ", {"text": ["Wind Velocity"], "type": "ui"}, " to control the direction and magnitude of the wind, and the ", {"text": ["Air Resistance"], "type": "ui"}, " to control the intensity of the wind on the ", {"text": ["POP Wind"], "fullpath": "/nodes/dop/popwind", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/dop/popwind"}, " node."]}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}, {"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [897, 948], "text": [{"tex